data.description: Welcome to this stunning listing! Nestled on a large private lot, this well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom turn-key ranch is a true gem, offering comfort and style.Step inside and be greeted by the beautifully updated kitchen with granite countertops, a single basin sink, and sleek black stainless steel appliances, creating a modern and sophisticated atmosphere that will inspire culinary delights.The meticulously landscaped and secluded backyard is a highlight of this property, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Imagine unwinding on the dual deck, enjoying the hot tub, and hosting memorable gatherings. RV/boat parking, a tool shed, and a detached large shop add convenience and storage.Speaking of the shop, it's a versatile space with a full bathroom, a bedroom/office, washer and dryer hookups, heating, and indoor/outdoor carpeting. It can be transformed into an ADU or mother-in-law suite, ideal for multi-generational living. Furthermore, it offers a potential rental income opportunity to maximize the property's potential.Ample parking ensures easy accommodation for guests and vehicles, eliminating any worries.Come and witness everything this remarkable home has to offer. From the beautiful upgrades and landscaped backyard to the versatile shop and potential rental income, it's truly a rare find. Don't miss the chance to make this house your dream home. Schedule a showing today! Home is being sold as is, small to minor repairs may be considered. Assumable VA loan, buyers to do their due diligence.
